*.tsbuildinfo
# dist/ is committed (root .gitignore allows it via the
# `!packages/repo-event-bridge/dist/` exception) so hub's
# file:../packages/repo-event-bridge install resolves built artifacts
# without needing a build step on consumer install.
#
# Mission-52 T3 revision v3 + methodology calibration #20: tried
# prepare-script in revision v2 — failed because cross-package file:
# refs in a non-workspaces monorepo are install-order-dependent (tsc
# runs before @ois/storage-provider is reachable in the package's
# local node_modules; install fails before dist/ can be built). Until
# idea-186 (npm workspaces) lands, committed dist/ is the lesser
# evil. See root .gitignore for the parallel storage-provider note.
